## Capture Summary

- **Flow recorded:** Sign in as admin → View KPI dashboard → Tour all 6 pages (campaigns, inventory, bookings, analytics) → Open campaign detail
- **Video specs:** H.264 codec, 1280×720, ~60s runtime, ~7.7 Mbps bitrate
- **Platform:** Headless Chromium via Playwright, live URL, no simulations
- **Data:** All screenshots show real dashboard data (8 campaigns, 31 inventory units, 101 bookings, 56 chart SVG elements)
- **Quality:** No console errors, smooth navigation, all pages load within 2s per transition

## Usage Notes

- Screenshots are numbered sequentially and depict the exact hero flow a prospect would experience
- Video captures deterministic clicks and transitions (good for replaying in async presentations)
- Login page screenshot shows the quick-demo-fill cards (admin role available with one click)
- All pages render responsive at 1280px (mobile-responsive design holds but primary capture is desktop)

## handoff
- produced: 7 hero-flow PNG screenshots + 1 deterministic video recording of full admin workflow (login through analytics)
- decisions: Captured admin role full tour; client role not recorded (proposal focuses on admin dashboard capabilities)
- next needs: proposal-writer will embed media URLs into deck + one-pager; use screenshot paths for visuals, hero-flow.webm for embedded video or GIF conversion
- risks: none — all media captures show live, functional app; no placeholder or mock data

